</style><p>此外，樱花葵的官方 YouTube 频道订阅人数已超过 10 万。首播后频道订阅人数突破10万的，仅限于所属经纪公司及部分公司旗下团体的艺人，对于个人艺人而言，这是史无前例的纪录。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="113892" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/independent-vtuber-aoi-sakura-made-a-strong-debut-with-100k-subscribers-and-59500-first-streaming-listeners/aoi_sakura_youtube_channel_february_5_2024/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/aoi_sakura_youtube_channel_february_5_2024.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="碧依 さくら Aoi Sakura" data-image-description="&lt;p>;碧依 さくら Aoi Sakura&lt;/p>;
